INTRODUCTION
~~~~~~~~~~~~
This game is a cross between the most excellent Scorched Tanks and the
almost as excellent M*A*S*H/Ant Wars. I would say it's a Worms clone, only
it's more like the above mentioned games then Worms.

It is for two players only (sorry!) as I've not yet had time to implement a
one player mode. These types of games are best played with two players
anyway.

