LOADING
~~~~~~~
This game can either be run from Workbench or CLI/Shell. There are two main
options for loading the game. Either you could straight forwardly click on
the icon or execute it from the Shell as a command line, in which case the
game will be run as normal, or you could do the following:

In your User-Startup or as a Shell command line, type:

Beasties sleep       * Option not available in this demo

(Instead of the usual "Beasties"). Now the game will automatically boot and
skip all intros, credits, etc, and automatically iconify. Cool eh? Once you
open the iconify bar, the game will run as normal. Useful for HD users who
wish the game to always be ready to run, but actually sit in the background
until they're ready to play it.

