COMPATIBILITY
~~~~~~~~~~~~~
This game should run on any Amiga with an Operating System of 2.0 or above
and 2 Meg of Chip Ram.

I've managed to test the game on the following setups:

Amiga 500+     2 Meg
Amiga 600      2 Meg
Amiga 1200     Unexpanded
Amiga 1200     2 Meg Chip, 6 Meg Fast & '30 CPU

Memory Note:
If you have installed the game onto your HD and upon running the game have
loads of windows open, colourful WB backdrops installed, WB Hacks wizzing
around, then you will obviously have less memory. The game constantly 
checks your memory status and if for any reason you reach 350 K or less,
immediately the game will no longer use any music of sound FX. So if you
suddenly find the game has no sound, it's not your TV! It just means
you're low on memory. 

Still, if you have more than 2 Meg to begin with, you 
will have no probs. The game itself actually only require 1.5 Meg, so every
user should be okay anyway. Just thought I should mention it!

